{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以黎明，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"与十夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"与偶数和奇数，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"与离去的黑夜，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"对于有理智者，此中有一种盟誓吗？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"难道你不知道你的主怎样惩治阿德人——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"有高柱的伊赖姆人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"像那样的人，在别的城市里还没有被创造过的——"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"怎样惩治在山谷里凿石为家的赛莫德人，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"怎样惩治有武力的法老。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"这等人曾在国中放肆，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"乃多行不义，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"故你的主把一种刑罚，倾注在他们身上。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你的主，确是监视的。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"至于人，当他的主考验他，故优待他，而且使他过安逸的生活的时候，他说：“我的主优待我了。”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"当他考验他，故节约他的给养的时候，他说：“我的主凌辱我了。”"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"绝不然！但你们不优待孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"你们不以济贫相勉励，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你们侵吞遗产，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"你们酷爱钱财。"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"绝不然！当大地震动复震动，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你的主和整列整列的天使，同齐来临的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":89,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"在那日，火狱将被拿来；在那日，人将觉悟，但觉悟于他有何裨益呢？"}]}